text: Calvary Cemetery is an Roman Catholic cemetery in South Portland, Maine, USA. ==Notable interments== * John Anglin (1850-1905), Medal of Honor recipient * Daniel Joseph Feeney (1894-1969), Roman Catholic Bishop * James Augustine Healy (1830-1900), Roman Catholic Bishop * Jane Callan Kilroy (1900-1975), politician * Kid Madden (1866-1896), professional baseball player ==References== Category:Roman Catholic Diocese of Portland Category:Buildings and structures in South Portland, Maine Category:Cemeteries in Cumberland County, Maine Category:Roman Catholic cemeteries in the United States
title: Calvary Cemetery (South Portland, Maine)
